NSCL-C 9/11 至 NSCL-C 11/11 • 参考文献 3：Sejpal S, et al.Early findings on toxicity of proton beam therapy with concurrent chemotherapy for non-small cell lung cancer.
Cancer 2011;117:3004-3013. 替换为 Gjyshi O, et al.Toxicity and survival after intensity-modulated proton therapy versus passive scattering proton therapy for NSCLC.J Thorac Oncol 2021;16:269-277. • 新增参考文献 30：Chang JY, et al.Stereotactic ablative radiotherapy for operable stage I non-small-cell lung cancer (revised STARS): long-term results of a single-arm, prospective trial with prespecified comparison to surgery.Lancet Oncol 2021;22:1448-1457. • 新增参考文献 34：Brooks ED, et al.Association of long-term outcomes and survival with multidisciplinary salvage treatment for local and regional recurrence after stereotactic ablative radiotherapy for early-stage lung cancer.JAMA Netw Open 2018;1:e181390. • 参考文献 86：Schild SE, et al.Toxicity related to radiotherapy dose and targeting strategy: a pooled analysis of cooperative group trials of combined modality therapy for locally advanced non-small cell lung cancer.J Thorac Oncol 2019;14:298-303. 替换为 Schild SE, et al.Exploring radiotherapy targeting strategy and dose: a pooled analysis of cooperative group trials of combined modality therapy for stage III NSCLC.J Thorac Oncol 2018;13:1171-1182. • 新增参考文献 88：Kong F-M S, et al.NRG-RTOG 1106/ACRIN 6697: A phase IIR trial of standard versus adaptive (mid-treatment PET-based) chemoradiotherapy for stage III NSCLC—Results and comparison to NRG-RTOG 0617 (non-personalized RT dose escalation).J Clin Oncol 2021;39:8548-8548. • 新增参考文献 103：Theelen WSME, et al.Pembrolizumab with or without radiotherapy for metastatic non-small-cell lung cancer: a polled analysis of two randomised trials.The Lancet 2021;9:467-475. NSCL-D • 评估 修改第 3 条：如果介入放射科医生或中心不能确定 IGTA 或使用 IGTA 治疗放射失败的可行性或安全性，可考虑另外从高流量专科中心征求介入放射科
意见。 • NSCLC 的消融 新增第 3 条：与手术一样，IGTA 后可能发生气胸，尤其是在一次治疗多个病变时。 据报道，气胸占 IGTA 病例的 18.7%–45.7%。不需要放置胸管的
自限性气胸是预期事件，除非需要加强护理，否则不将其视为并发症。在 20.7% 的 IGTA 病例中，可能需要插入胸管。 新增参考文献 10：Genshaft SJ, Suh RD, Abtin F, et al.Society of Interventional Radiology Quality Improvement Standards on Percutaneous
Ablation of Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer and Metastatic Disease to the Lungs.J Vasc Interv Radiol 2021;32:1242.e1-1242.e10. NSCL-E 1/2 • 既往辅助化疗或无资格进行铂类化疗 接受既往辅助化疗或无资格接受铂类化疗的 EGFR 突变阳性（外显子 19 缺失、L858R）且完全切除的 IIB-IIIA 期或高危 IB-IIIA 期 NSCLC 患者使用奥
希替尼。 NSCL-F 1/2 • 无法切除、PS 01、≥2 周期根治性同步放化疗后无疾病进展的 II/III 期 NSCLC 患者的巩固免疫治疗 • 修改脚注 §： 如果使用德瓦鲁单抗，如果患者未在放疗同时接受全剂量化疗，则不推荐再进行 2 个周期化疗。

