29 Perol M, Chouaid C, Perol D, et al. Randomized, phase III study of gemcitabine or erlotinib maintenance therapy versus observation, with predefined second-line treatment, after cisplatingemcitabine induction chemotherapy in advanced non-small celll lung cancer.J Clin Oncol 2012;30:3516-3524.
